/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%C3%B9-H%E1%BB%AFu/Mi%E1%BA%BFn-Mi%E1%BA%BFn/poem-0JpgnJdh4Zbo-dcKwizr1g">Miến Miến - 盼盼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%C3%B9-H%E1%BB%AFu/author-ZjSu27nDCKsyKWbOwBvzWw">Cù Hữu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-L%C3%B4i-Ph%C3%A1t/%C3%94-%C3%B4-ca/poem--nkwKog4rhovNtymFbWpRg">Ô ô ca - 烏烏歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-L%C3%B4i-Ph%C3%A1t/author-5J0P_EDGEC1h1gar2eA3WQ">Nhạc Lôi Phát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/Ph%C3%B3ng-ng%C3%B4n/poem-eVvgjy2SreWudA8ciPrP7A">Phóng ngôn - 放言</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-lCIs61Hzjl6rqKSiwGq6ow">Nguyên Hiếu Vấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%C3%B4-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-h8vI1vZwJXnKjUVY3CFMoA">Thương Ngô tức sự - 蒼梧即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-M%C3%B4n-ph%C3%BA/poem-NExLx3ZnSypitVJgFbFpOA">Trường Môn phú - 長門賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0/author-HC1oHxsir20vL_KcVXiEhQ">Tư Mã Tương Như</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
